---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="My Expertise | Call Brad" description="Javier's expertise in privacy compliance, GDPR, and data protection services.">
  
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-montserrat text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">My Expertise</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Specialized knowledge and services to help your business navigate data protection and privacy compliance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Expertise Cards -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        
        <!-- Privacy Programs -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">Privacy Programs</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                I can develop robust Privacy Programs tailored to your business needs, ensuring compliance with GDPR and other relevant regulations. I can provide a solid foundation for data protection and privacy management.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Processing Agreements -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">Data Processing Agreements</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                My expertise includes drafting and reviewing Data Processing Agreements to meet stringent data protection standards. I ensure these agreements safeguard your business and comply with legal requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- EU and US Privacy Laws -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">EU and US Privacy Laws</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                I have extensive knowledge of both EU and US Privacy Laws, including GDPR and CCPA. My expertise ensures your business remains compliant across jurisdictions, providing comprehensive support for international data protection needs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DPIAs and Data Transfers -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">DPIAs and Data Transfers</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                I can conduct Data Protection Impact Assessments and assess data transfer mechanisms to ensure they comply with GDPR and other international data protection regulations. I can help mitigate privacy risks and maintain compliance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Employee Training -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">Employee Training</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                I offer comprehensive training sessions to educate your staff on data protection practices and compliance requirements. I try to empower employees with the knowledge needed to handle personal data responsibly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Need help with any of these areas?</p>
        <a href="https://app.usemotion.com/meet/javier-kr40/30min-Call-Brad" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#2b2e83] text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-[#232465] transition-colors">
          Get in Touch
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[#2b2e83] font-medium hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
